    &gt;市场需求强劲！新一代FMCW激光雷达技术或成车企争先“新赛点”&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NjAxNjU0OA==&amp;amp;mid=2247503451&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=e8e10b0884204f300627b1808abd030b&amp;amp;chksm=e9473110de30b806fda5c7563ca22d2c923178ea76f2d0d4729926ed47aead92a2d5e6e2b0e2&amp;amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
